@qinliujie Sometimes container.stop() may throw exceptions, 
it denpends on how you want shutdown the application: 
- I prefer to solve the exceptions, and shutdown again;
- If running.countDown() is outside of the loop,  main thread is stopped while container is still running, then the application is in a very strange status.

参考 #333 .

我们这边的做法是由自动部署系统触发一个停机消息，然后应用主动调用销毁方法进行优雅停机的。

